{"type":"message","id":"0df5279c","parentId":"1d2ad641","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:11:24.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is relaying a scheduled reminder about the WHOOP Health Integration project. It's Friday, March 13th at 1:11 PM HKT, which is after Guillermo's typically mentioned early morning times but still during the workday.\n\nThe reminder notes:\n- Paused Mar 6 (exactly 7 days ago as mentioned)\n- Guillermo asked to check back in 7 days\n- Still waiting for CLIENT_ID + CLIENT_SECRET from developer.whoop.com\n\nThis is a legitimate reminder that I should relay to Guillermo. According to SOUL.md, I should be direct and brief. According to MEMORY.md, the WHOOP project is a P2 task with the spec in Notion (31939dd6...).\n\nI should:\n1. Acknowledge the reminder\n2. Keep it brief and actionable\n3. Reference what's needed\n4. Suggest next steps\n\nLet me send this to Guillermo via the channel (which is Discord based on the inbound context).","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Hey — WHOOP Health Integration check-in time! 🏃\n\n**Status:** Still paused waiting on your end.\n\n**What we need:** CLIENT_ID + CLIENT_SECRET from https://developer.whoop.com (your Whoop developer account)\n\nOnce you grab those, the integration can move forward. Notion spec is ready (`31939dd6...`).\n\nWant to pull those creds now, or should I ping again next week?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":347,"cacheRead":9459,"cacheWrite":21599,"totalTokens":31415,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0017350000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0009459000000000001,"cacheWrite":0.026998750000000002,"total":0.02968965}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773378679361}}
