{"type":"message","id":"9e977a16","parentId":"a5813be1","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:09:55.329Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've sent April the fix. The issue is the `tools.profile: \"coding\"` which filters out the message tool. She needs to either switch to `\"assistant\"` profile or add explicit `\"allow\": [\"message\"]` to override.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**Root cause:** `tools.profile: \"coding\"` excludes messaging tools.\n\n**Fix:** Either switch to `\"assistant\"` profile or add `\"allow\": [\"message\"]` override.\n\nSent her instructions. Should be a quick config edit + restart."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":8,"output":124,"cacheRead":43985,"cacheWrite":826,"totalTokens":44943,"cost":{"input":0.00004,"output":0.0031000000000000003,"cacheRead":0.021992499999999998,"cacheWrite":0.0051625,"total":0.030295}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773392991416}}
