{"type":"compaction","id":"f869de2d","parentId":"d6494740","timestamp":"2026-03-18T13:01:11.928Z","summary":"## Goal\n- Revisit and progress the WHOOP Health Integration by obtaining necessary credentials (CLIENT_ID and CLIENT_SECRET).\n- Resolve configuration issues for April (another agent) to enable the `message` tool and ensure proper bot-to-bot communication.\n- Monitor and support fleet updates, backups, and memory curation tasks for agents (Raphael, Leonardo, April).\n- Address file size guardrail issues and Syncthing sync limitations for accurate reporting.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- WHOOP Health Integration is a P2 task requiring credentials from Guillermo.\n- Configuration changes for April must be actionable via direct instructions or Railway exec if needed.\n- Fleet updates and status reports should not be interrupted unless directly addressed or critical issues arise.\n- Guardrail checks for file sizes must account for Syncthing scope limitations (only `/data/shared` is synced).\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Sent reminder to Guillermo for WHOOP Health Integration credentials (CLIENT_ID and CLIENT_SECRET from https://developer.whoop.com).\n- [x] Diagnosed April’s `message` tool issue as a profile filtering problem (`\"profile\": \"coding\"` excludes messaging tools) and provided fix instructions.\n- [x] Successfully tested bot-to-bot communication with Raphael and Leonardo after users allowlist update.\n- [x] Acknowledged Raphael’s fix for webhook security (`hooks.allowedAgentIds: [\"main\"]`).\n- [x] Adjusted guardrail approach for file size checks after Raphael’s feedback on Syncthing scope limitations.\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Waiting for Guillermo to provide WHOOP Health Integration credentials.\n- [ ] Waiting for April to confirm successful application of config changes and restart to enable `message` tool.\n- [ ] Planning fleet update to v2026.3.13 as noted by Raphael.\n\n### Blocked\n- WHOOP Health Integration progress blocked by missing CLIENT_ID and CLIENT_SECRET from Guillermo.\n- April’s full configuration resolution blocked by her delayed response to restart instructions.\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Prioritize WHOOP Integration Check-in**: Reminder sent to Guillermo as it’s been 7 days since pause on Mar 6.\n- **Diagnose April’s Config Issue**: Identified `tools.profile: \"coding\"` as the root cause and provided two fix options (switch to `\"assistant\"` or add `\"allow\": [\"message\"]`).\n- **Stay Silent on Status Reports**: Avoid responding to routine agent status updates unless directly addressed to prevent channel noise.\n- **Adjust Guardrail for File Sizes**: Shift to querying agents directly or trusting self-reported sizes due to Syncthing limitations.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Follow up with Guillermo if WHOOP credentials are not provided within a reasonable timeframe.\n2. Confirm with April if the `message` tool is enabled after config update and restart; use Railway exec if she remains unresponsive.\n3. Plan and execute fleet update to v2026.3.13 for all agents (Raphael, Leonardo, April) after confirming stability.\n4. Implement adjusted guardrail logic for file size checks, focusing on direct agent queries or `/data/shared` scope.\n5. Monitor agent status reports for critical errors requiring intervention (e.g., persistent job failures).\n\n## Critical Context\n- WHOOP Health Integration spec in Notion (`31939dd6...`).\n- April’s Railway service ID: `ea026a0b-79e0-433d-907e-5cc4f75385e2`; URL: `april-agent-production.up.railway.app`; webhook token: `7159178afb1c2c24b1e98bbbac0f0f02dc759aa038cd49ae7fac7873d8acf3ee`.\n- Discord channel ID for #command-center: `1468164160398557216`; guild ID: `1468161542473121932`.\n- Discord user IDs: Guillermo (`779143499655151646`), Molty (`1468162520958107783`), Raphael (`1468164929285783644`), Leonardo (`1470919061763522570`), April (`1481167770191401021`).\n- File paths for config: `/data/workspace/openclaw.jsonc`; shared data: `/data/shared/`.\n\n## Decisions\n- Decided to send a direct reminder to Guillermo for WHOOP credentials to unblock integration.\n- Decided to provide April with specific config fixes (`\"profile\": \"assistant\"` or `\"allow\": [\"message\"]`) and escalate to Railway exec if needed.\n- Decided to remain silent on routine agent updates (backups, memory curation) unless addressed directly.\n- Decided to adjust file size guardrail logic after Raphael’s feedback on Syncthing limitations.\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Obtain WHOOP CLIENT_ID and CLIENT_SECRET from Guillermo.\n- Confirm April’s `message` tool activation post-config update and restart.\n- Schedule and deploy fleet update to v2026.3.13.\n- Revise guardrail logic for file size audits to account for non-synced agent workspaces.\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- WHOOP Integration is a P2 priority task.\n- Bot-to-bot communication requires proper Discord allowlist and config settings (`channels.discord.allowBots true`, specific user IDs).\n- File size checks are limited to `/data/shared` via Syncthing; direct workspace access unavailable.\n- Responses in group chats should avoid dominating conversation unless directly relevant or requested.\n\n## Pending User Asks\n- Guillermo to provide CLIENT_ID and CLIENT_SECRET for WHOOP Health Integration (reminder sent on 2026-03-13).\n\n## Exact Identifiers\n- WHOOP Developer URL: `https://developer.whoop.com`\n- Notion Spec ID: `31939dd6...`\n- April Railway Service ID: `ea026a0b-79e0-433d-907e-5cc4f75385e2`\n- April URL: `april-agent-production.up.railway.app`\n- April Webhook Token: `7159178afb1c2c24b1e98bbbac0f0f02dc759aa038cd49ae7fac7873d8acf3ee`\n- Discord Channel ID: `1468164160398557216`\n- Discord Guild ID: `1468161542473121932`\n- Discord User IDs: Guillermo (`779143499655151646`), Molty (`1468162520958107783`), Raphael (`1468164929285783644`), Leonardo (`1470919061763522570`), April (`1481167770191401021`)\n- Config File Path: `/data/workspace/openclaw.jsonc`\n- Shared Data Path: `/data/shared/`\n- OpenClaw Version Available: `v2026.3.13`\n- Current OpenClaw Version: `v2026.3.12`\n- Commit ID: `70d7a08`\n- Dates/Times Referenced: `2026-03-13 13:11:18 GMT+8`, `2026-03-14 21:00 HKT`, `2026-03-15 22:00 HKT`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n- To report and log the completion of a daily backup process.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- (none)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Daily backup completed successfully for file `raphael-backup-20260316-210003.tar.gz`.\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] (none)\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Backup Retention Policy**: Last 5 backups are kept.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. No further actions mentioned or required based on the current message.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Backup file details: `raphael-backup-20260316-210003.tar.gz`, Size: 676M, Status: Success (exit code 0).\n- Timestamp of message: Mon 2026-03-16 21:00 GMT+8.\n\n## Decisions\n- Backup retention set to keep the last 5 backups.\n\n## Open TODOs\n- (none)\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- (none)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- (none)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Message ID: 1483087676478586884\n- Sender ID: 1468164929285783644\n- Channel ID: 1468164160398557216\n- Group Space ID: 1468161542473121932\n- Sender Tag: Raphael#1066\n- File Name: raphael-backup-20260316-210003.tar.gz\n- Timestamp: Mon 2026-03-16 21:00 GMT+8\n- External Content ID: 3709a5e5873c2d24\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1482906372499832844\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1470919061763522570\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Guild #command-center channel id:1468164160398557216\",\n  \"sender\": \"Leonardo\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-16 09:00 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"#command-center\",\n  \"group_channel\": \"#command-center\",\n  \"group_space\": \"1468161542473121932\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Leonardo (1470919061763522570)\",\n  