{"type":"message","id":"a3ed47d7","parentId":"0b41788d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:31:48.938Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Here's what changed:\n\n**1. Nightly curation cron (23:00 HKT)** — now has mandatory PARA demotion protocol. Before trimming anything from MEMORY.md, it must:\n- Classify each item (Project/Area/Resource/Archive)\n- Write to the correct vault path with metadata header\n- Only then remove from MEMORY.md\n- Report what was demoted in the Discord summary\n\n**2. AGENTS.md** — replaced the old \"Memory\" section with a 5-layer architecture table showing the full hierarchy and the \"trimming = moving, not deleting\" rule.\n\n**3. PARA-GUIDE.md** — added the nightly demotion flow alongside the existing weekly curation.\n\nThe flow is now:\n```\nMEMORY.md full → demote to vault/knowledge/ → searchable via memory_search forever\n```\n\nTonight's 23:00 run will be the first with the new protocol. I'll watch the output."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":229,"cacheRead":90037,"cacheWrite":528,"totalTokens":90795,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.005725,"cacheRead":0.045018499999999996,"cacheWrite":0.0033,"total":0.05404849999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773880301949}}
